## Development

### Database Migrations

```bash
# Create migration
pnpm prisma migrate dev --name <migration-name>

# Apply migrations
pnpm prisma migrate deploy

# Reset database
pnpm prisma migrate reset
```

### Testing

```bash
pnpm test           # Watch mode
pnpm test:coverage  # With coverage
```

## Docker

